e in two decades.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Ditto for Credit Su=
isse. It finalized the sale this week of an offering backing Lone Star Fund=
s=E2=80=99 acquisition of chemicals distribution company Manuchar NV at the=
 largest discount in a decade for the European market: 86 cents on the euro=
. =E2=80=A6</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CBanks agreed to financ=
e deals months ago and we=E2=80=99ve had a massive shift in expectations,=
=E2=80=9D said Nichole Hammond, a senior portfolio manager at Angel Oak Cap=
ital Advisors. =E2=80=9CThe uncertain economic backdrop is causing investor=
s to be much more selective and they want to be paid more for the risks the=
y are taking.=E2=80=9D</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">This is=
